# Build artefacts (anywhere in the tree).
*.agdai
*.aux
*.log
*.out
*~

# Handoff notes / internal markdown are kept locally but not tracked.
# (The root README.md is exempted by the whitelist below.)
*.md

# Whitelist policy: only the following files/dirs are tracked.
#   /BRA2/           -- the active Agda codebase (incl. BRA2/godelI-II-summary.pdf)
#   /bra-godelII.tex -- the project paper / writeup
#   /README.md       -- public project README
#
# Everything else (including CLAUDE.md, BRA/ legacy edition, BRA2/*.md
# handoff notes, root-level reference PDFs, build artefacts, and /old/)
# is untracked.

/*

!/.gitignore
!/BRA2/
!/bra-godelII.tex
!/README.md
